                                  Exercise & Activity Plan
                               </h4>
                               <p className="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-medium italic bg-gray-50/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 whitespace-pre-line">{currentResult.exercisePlan}</p>
                            </div>
